7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素</h2>\n<h3 id=\"语义元素\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"语义元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>语义元素</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>HTML 语义化标签</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#x3C;article></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;aside></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;details></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;figcaption></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;figure></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;footer></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;header></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;main></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;mark></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;nav></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;section></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;summary></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;time></code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"音视频元素\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%9F%B3%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"音视频元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>音视频元素</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#x3C;audio></code></li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;video></code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"表单优化内置数据校验\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A1%A8%E5%8D%95%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C\" aria-label=\"表单优化内置数据校验 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>表单优化：内置数据校验</h3>\n<p>校验属性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>type</code>: <code>&#x3C;input type=\"email\"></code></li>\n<li><code>required</code></li>\n<li><code>pattern</code>: 正则校验</li>\n<li><code>min / max</code></li>\n<li><code>minlength / maxlength</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>校验效果</p>\n<ul>\n<li>通过：CSS 伪类 <code>:valid</code> ，提交数据</li>\n<li>不通过：CSS 伪类 <code>:invalid</code> ，显示错误信息并阻止提交</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"iframe-增强安全性和渲染\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#iframe-%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93\" aria-label=\"iframe 增强安全性和渲染 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>iframe 增强安全性和渲染</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>sandbox</code> 对 frame 中的内容添加额外限制，如 <code>allow-downloads</code> <code>allow-same-origin</code> <code>allow-scripts</code> 等</li>\n<li>seamless: 无缝嵌入 iframe</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>srcdoc</code> 直接嵌入内联 HTML 文本，如:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">var iframe = document.createElement(\"iframe\")\niframe.srcdoc = `&#x3C;!DOCTYPE html>&#x3C;p>Hello World!&#x3C;/p>`\ndocument.body.appendChild(iframe)\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"mathml\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mathml\" aria-label=\"mathml permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MathML</h3>\n<p>参考 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Authoring\">MDN-MathML</a></p>\n<p>支持使用 MathML 书写数学公式：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;math>\n  &#x3C;msqrt>\n    &#x3C;mn>2&#x3C;/mn>\n  &#x3C;/msqrt>\n&#x3C;/math>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"通信\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1\" aria-label=\"通信 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>通信</h2>\n<h3 id=\"websockets\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#websockets\" aria-label=\"websockets permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WebSockets</h3>\n<p>客户端和服务器建立持久的 TCP 连接，用得比较多了不再赘述。</p>\n<h3 id=\"server-sent-eventssse\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#server-sent-eventssse\" aria-label=\"server sent eventssse permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Server-Sent Events(SSE)</h3>\n<p>允许服务器向客户端推送事件，可用于数据仪表盘、实时股票价格展示等场景。</p>\n<h3 id=\"webrtc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webrtc\" aria-label=\"webrtc permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WebRTC</h3>\n<p>浏览器之间建立点对点通信，可用于实时音视频和数据共享等场景。</p>\n<h2 id=\"离线与存储\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%A6%BB%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8\" aria-label=\"离线与存储 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>离线与存储</h2>\n<h3 id=\"在线离线事件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%A8%E7%BA%BF%E7%A6%BB%E7%BA%BF%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"在线离线事件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>在线/离线事件</h3>\n<p>读取属性值: <code>navigator.online: boolean</code></p>\n<p><code>ononline</code> / <code>onoffline</code> 事件注册：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>事件注册：在 window, document 或 document.body 上 <code>addEventListener(\"ononline\", fn);</code></li>\n<li>事件函数: <code>document.[body.]ononline = function(){...}</code></li>\n<li>内联事件: <code>&#x3C;body ononline=\"fn1()\" onoffline=\"fn2()\"></code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"dom-storage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dom-storage\" aria-label=\"dom storage permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DOM Storage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>LocalStorage：同域跨浏览器窗口和选项卡共享</li>\n<li>SessionStorage：仅本次会话可用</li>\n<li>GlobalStorage(仅 Firefox)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"indexeddb\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#indexeddb\" aria-label=\"indexeddb permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IndexedDB</h3>\n<p>用于在浏览器端存储大量结构化数据的事务型数据库系统。</p>\n<p>可以和 <strong>Web Workers</strong> 结合使用以提高性能。</p>\n<p>可用于构建 <strong>PWA</strong>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"file-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#file-api\" aria-label=\"file api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>File API</h3>\n<p>文件上传：<code>&#x3C;input type=\"file\" multiple onchange=\"handleFiles(this.files)\"></code></p>\n<p>ObjectURL:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>window.URL.createObjectURL(file)</code> 创建 ObjectURL 使得文件可以通过 URL 来引用(如 a、img 元素等)</li>\n<li><code>window.URL.revokeObjectURL(objURL)</code> ObjectURL 使用完毕后应释放</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"多媒体\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%9A%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93\" aria-label=\"多媒体 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>多媒体</h2>\n<p>上文已提到过的:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#x3C;audio></code> 与 <code>&#x3C;video></code></li>\n<li>WebRTC</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"camera-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#camera-api\" aria-label=\"camera api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Camera API</h3>\n<p>调用系统自带相机: <code>&#x3C;input type=\"file\" id=\"take-picture\" accept=\"image/*\"></code></p>\n<h3 id=\"track-和-webvtt\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#track-%E5%92%8C-webvtt\" aria-label=\"track 和 webvtt permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Track 和 WebVTT</h3>\n<p>用于时序文本或其他基于时间的数据, 如视频字幕等.</p>\n<p><code>&#x3C;track></code>元素作为 <code>&#x3C;audio></code> 和 <code>&#x3C;video></code> 元素的子元素,用于指定时序文本字幕.</p>\n<p>WebVTT 表示 Web 视频文本字幕格式(.vtt).</p>\n<h2 id=\"图像与效果\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C\" aria-label=\"图像与效果 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>图像与效果</h2>\n<h3 id=\"canvas-text-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#canvas-text-api\" aria-label=\"canvas text api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Canvas Text API</h3>\n<p>新增 <code>fillText()</code> 和 <code>strokeText()</code> 方法</p>\n<h3 id=\"webgl-3d\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webgl-3d\" aria-label=\"webgl 3d permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WebGL 3D</h3>\n<p>用于特定领域, 这里不做详述.</p>\n<h3 id=\"svg\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#svg\" aria-label=\"svg permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SVG</h3>\n<p>基于 XML 语法的矢量图, 可用于绘制简单的 LOGO 或流程图绘制等场景.</p>\n<h2 id=\"性能与集成\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8E%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"性能与集成 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>性能与集成</h2>\n<h3 id=\"web-workers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#web-workers\" aria-label=\"web workers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Web Workers</h3>\n<p>创建后台线程执行一个 JS 文件, 一般用于执行大量耗时的计算任务.</p>\n<h3 id=\"xmlhttprequest-level-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#xmlhttprequest-level-2\" aria-label=\"xmlhttprequest level 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>XMLHttpRequest Level 2</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>支持 <code>timeout</code> 超时设定</li>\n<li>支持使用 FormData 对象管理表单数据</li>\n<li>支持文件上传</li>\n<li>支持跨域请求</li>\n<li>支持获取二进制数据</li>\n<li>支持数据传输进度信息</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"history-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#history-api\" aria-label=\"history api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>History API</h3>\n<p><code>window.history</code> 对象提供了一些有用的方法来操作浏览器访问历史:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>history.back()</code></li>\n<li><code>history.forward()</code></li>\n<li><code>history.go()</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"contenteditable\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contenteditable\" aria-label=\"contenteditable permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ContentEditable</h3>\n<p>可编辑元素, 可用于实现富文本编辑器, 详情查看另一篇文章 &#x3C;在线编辑器实现浅析>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"拖拽-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8B%96%E6%8B%BD-api\" aria-label=\"拖拽 api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>拖拽 API</h3>\n<p>用于实现拖拽元素, 主要包括 <code>ondrop</code> <code>ondrag</code> <code>ondragstart</code> <code>ondragend</code> <code>ondragenter</code> <code>ondragleave</code> 等事件及相关属性方法.</p>\n<h3 id=\"焦点管理\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%84%A6%E7%82%B9%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86\" aria-label=\"焦点管理 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>焦点管理</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>document.activeElement</code> 查找当前聚焦的 Element</li>\n<li><code>document.hasFocus</code> 判断当前元素是否是焦点</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"基于-web-的协议处理程序\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E-web-%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F\" aria-label=\"基于 web 的协议处理程序 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基于 Web 的协议处理程序</h3>\n<p>实现在 Web 中可以使用非 HTTP 协议将网页链接到其他资源, 如发邮件等.</p>\n<p>属于特定领域功能, 用到时再研究.</p>\n<h3 id=\"动画渲染控制\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%BB%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" aria-label=\"动画渲染控制 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>动画渲染控制</h3>\n<p><code>window.requestAnimationFrame(callback)</code> 执行动画, 并在下一次浏览器重绘前调用 callback.</p>\n<p>一般 callback 会更新动画, 用于在不同的渲染时机中触发不同的动画.</p>\n<h3 id=\"全屏-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%8F-api\" aria-label=\"全屏 api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>全屏 API</h3>\n<p><code>element.requestFullscreen()</code>\n<code>document.exitFullscreen()</code>\n<code>document.onfullscreenchange</code>\n<code>document.onfullscreenerror</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"鼠标锁定-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%E9%94%81%E5%AE%9A-api\" aria-label=\"鼠标锁定 api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>鼠标锁定 API</h3>\n<p>使鼠标指针不离开指定区域, 如游戏场景中, 鼠标指针移到最左侧后, 鼠标不会移出游戏窗口, 而是保持在边缘移动画面.</p>\n<p>兼容性问题: 只有 Chrome 和 Firefox 实现了有限功能.</p>\n<h2 id=\"设备访问\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE\" aria-label=\"设备访问 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设备访问</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Camera API 见上文</li>\n<li>鼠标锁定 API 见上文</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"触摸事件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A6%E6%91%B8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"触摸事件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>触摸事件</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>TouchEvent 界面触摸状态发生变化时的事件回调</li>\n<li>Touch 单个触摸对象</li>\n<li>TouchList 一组触摸对象, 如多点触摸时</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"地理位置-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE-api\" aria-label=\"地理位置 api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>地理位置 API</h3>\n<p><code>navigator.geolocation</code> 对象提供了一套地理相关 API:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()</code> 获取设备当前位置</li>\n<li><code>Geolocation.watchPosition()</code> 设备位置改变时的触发事件</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"设备方向\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91\" aria-label=\"设备方向 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设备方向</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>deviceorientation</code> 设备方向改变时的触发事件</li>\n<li><code>devicemotion</code> 设备移动时的触发事件</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"css\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css\" aria-label=\"css permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS</h2>\n<h3 id=\"background\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#background\" aria-label=\"background permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Background</h3>\n<p>已经用得很普遍了.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>box-shadow</code> 阴影</li>\n<li><code>background</code> 属性支持多背景</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"border\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#border\" aria-label=\"border permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Border</h3>\n<p>同样早就用过</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>border-image</code></li>\n<li><code>border-radius</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"css-animations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-animations\" aria-label=\"css animations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS Animations</h3>\n<p>CSS 动画的灵活性和可玩性都极大, 后面会专门抽时间研究一下.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Animations\">MDN - CSS Animations</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"排版相关\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8E%92%E7%89%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3\" aria-label=\"排版相关 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>排版相关</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>文字溢出处理: <code>text-overflow</code></li>\n<li>\n<p>连字符(长单词)处理: <code>hyphens</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>hyphens 属性值</li>\n</ul>\n<p>hyphens: none; 单词不断行\nhyphens: manual; 有连字符时换行\nhyphens: auto; 浏览器自动处理</p>\n</li>\n<li>文字阴影: <code>text-shadow</code></li>\n<li>文字装饰(下划线/中划线): <code>text-decoration</code></li>\n<li>指定在线字体: <code>@font-face</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"多列布局\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%9A%E5%88%97%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80\" aria-label=\"多列布局 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>多列布局</h3>\n<p>参考: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/CSS_layout/Multiple-column_Layout\">MDN-多列布局</a></p>\n<p><code>column-count: n;</code> 设置后浏览器自动将当前元素分为 n 列</p>\n<p><code>column-width: 200px;</code> 最小列宽</p>\n<p><code>columns: n 200px;</code> 合并列数与列宽设置</p>\n<p><code>column-gap: 20px;</code> 列间隙, 默认 1em</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"HTML5技术扫盲","date":"May 11, 2020","description":"HTML5标准新特性概览"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/typescript-type-guards/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TypeScript Type Guards"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/html-pick/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"HTML拾遗"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"7e8300d3-7450-56f6-9160-2f8a0da57a8b","previousPostId":"418fed14-5d5e-52d4-947e-9bc82b303e7c","nextPostId":"46cc66f3-833c-5166-849a-0e121fc2815c"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}